<ref>{{cite journal | doi =10.1126/science.1219861 | pmid =22773140 | title =Absence of Detectable Arsenate in DNA from Arsenate-Grown GFAJ-1 Cells | journal =Science | volume =337 | issue =6093 | pages =470 | year =2012 | last1 =Reaves | first1 =M. L. | last2 =Sinha | first2 =S. | last3 =Rabinowitz | first3 =J. D. | last4 =Kruglyak | first4 =L. | last5 =Redfield | first5 =R. J. | bibcode =2012Sci...337..470R }}</ref><ref name="Westheimer">{{Cite journal |last=Westheimer |first=F.H. |authorlink=Frank Westheimer |title=Why nature chose phosphates |journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] |volume=235 |issue=4793 |pages=1173–1178 (see pp. 1175–1176) |date=6 June 1987 |url=http://academic.evergreen.edu/curricular/m2o2006/seminar/westheimer.pdf |doi=10.1126/science.2434996 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616182714/http://academic.evergreen.edu/curricular/m2o2006/seminar/westheimer.pdf |archivedate=2011年6月16日 }}</ref>

=== 人类产生的砷化合物 ===

人类产生的砷化合物和自然界中的一样，主要是砷的氧化物和含氧酸根，来源包括矿区废水和畜禽养殖场。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Nordstrom DK |title=Worldwide occurrences of arsenic in ground water |journal=Science |year=2002 |volume=296 |issue=5576 |page=2143 |doi=10.1126/science.1072375}}</ref> 例如许多矿石（尤其是[[硫化物|硫化物]]）含有砷，[[煅烧|煅烧]]时[[砷化物|砷化物]]转变为高温下易[[挥发|挥发]]的[[三氧化二砷|三氧化二砷]]，然后排入大气。畜禽养殖场在[[饲料|饲料]]中大量使用[[抗生素|抗生素]][[洛克沙砷|洛克沙砷]]。<ref>{{cite news |last=Hileman |first=B |title=Arsenic in Chicken Production |publisher=Chemical and Engineering News |date=9 April 2007 |pages=34–35}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Helena | last = Bottemiller | title = Bill Introduced to Ban Arsenic Antibiotics in Feed | date = 26 September 2009 | url = http://www.foodsafetynews.com/2009/09/bill-introduced-to-ban-arsenic-antibiotics-in-feed/ | work = Food Safety News | accessdate = 2011-01-10 | archive-date = 2011-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110125092001/http://www.foodsafetynews.com/2009/09/bill-introduced-to-ban-arsenic-antibiotics-in-feed/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 一些木材要用[[防腐剂|防腐剂]][[砷酸铜|砷酸铜]]进行处理。这些砷源影响下游生物的方式还不清楚，但可能为数众多，其中[[甲基化|甲基化]]是最常被引述的途径。<ref name='Biomethylation'>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1248/jhs.49.171 | title = Biomethylation of Arsenic is Essentially Detoxicating Event | journal = Journal of Health Science | year = 2003 | author = Sakurai T | volume = 49 | issue = 3 | pages = 171–178 | url = http://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jhs/49/3/49_171/_article/-char/en | accessdate = 2011-01-10}}</ref>

==== 含砷药物 ====
尽管人们很早就知道砷的毒性，或者说正因为如此，正规的[[药学|药学]]和[[庸医|庸医]]对含砷药剂的使用已有历史，而且延续至21世纪。<ref>{{Cite journal |author1=Jun Zhu |author2=Zhu Chen |author3=Valérie Lallemand-Breitenbach |author4=Hugues de Thé |title=How Acute Promyelocytic Leukaemia Revived Arsenic |journal=[[Nature_Reviews_Cancer|Nature Reviews Cancer]] |year=2002 |volume=2 |issue=9 |pages=705–714 |doi=10.1038/nrc887 |pmid=12209159 |url=http://www.nature.com/nrc/journal/v2/n9/full/nrc887.html |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-09-27 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019122755/https://www.nature.com/nrc/journal/v2/n9/full/nrc887.html }}</ref><ref name='ITOM'>{{Cite journal |last1=Gibaud |first1=Stéphane |last2=Jaouen |first2=Gérard |title=Arsenic - based drugs: from Fowler's solution to modern anticancer chemotherapy |url=http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-642-13185-1_1 |journal=[http://www.springer.com/series/3418 Topics in Organometallic Chemistry] |year=2010 |volume=32 |pages=1–20 |doi=10.1007/978-3-642-13185-1_1 |series=Topics in Organometallic Chemistry |isbn=978-3-642-13184-4 |access-date=2015-07-30 |archive-date=2015-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226002809/http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-642-13185-1_1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 从19世纪至20世纪，市场上可以买到{{link-en|福勒溶液|Fowler's solution}}（一种有毒的[[亚砷酸钾|亚砷酸钾]]溶液）。由德国化学家[[保罗·埃尔利希|保罗·埃尔利希]]发现的有机砷化合物[[洒尔佛散|洒尔佛散]]是第一种[[化学合成|合成]]的抗[[梅毒|梅毒]]药剂，也可用于[[化疗|化疗]]。<ref name=ITOM/>不过这种疗法有很多问题，会产生长期并发症，所以1943年前后终于被[[青霉素|青霉素]]取代。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2790789/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-07-30 |archive-date=2015-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406054327/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2790789/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[体外|体外]]研究表明[[三氧化二砷|三氧化二砷]]（As<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>）能通过阻滞[[细胞周期|细胞周期]]和触发[[细胞死亡|细胞死亡]]的方式抑制[[多发性骨髓瘤|多发性骨髓瘤]]细胞的增生。<ref name=Woo>{{cite journal | title = Arsenic Trioxide-mediated Growth Inhibition in MC/CAR Myeloma Cells via Cell Cycle Arrest in Association with Induction of Cyclin-dependent Kinase Inhibitor, p21, and Apoptosis | journal = Cancer Research | last1 = Park | date = June 6, 2000 | first = Woo H. Park | pages = 3065–71 | author2 = Jae G. Seol | author3 = Eun S. Kim | author4 = Jung M. Hyun | author5 = Chul W. Jung | author6 = Chung C. Lee | author7 = Byoung K. Kim | author8 = Young Y. Lee | pmid = 10850458 | volume = 60 | issue = 3065 | url = http://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/60/11/3065.full | accessdate = 2010-12-15 | archive-date = 2017-10-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171002120545/http://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/60/11/3065.full | dead-url = no }}</ref> 这项研究成果显示三氧化二砷临床上可能对多发性骨髓瘤<ref name=Woo/>或[[白血病|白血病]]<ref>{{cite journal | title = Treatment with arsenic trioxide (ATO) and MEK1 inhibitor activates the p73-p53AIP1 apoptotic pathway in leukemia cells | last1 = Lunghi | journal = Blood | date = 15 July 2004 | first = Paolo Lunghi | author2 = Antonio Costanzo | author3 = Massimo Levrero | author4 = Antonio Bonati | pmid = 15031205 | volume = 104 | issue = 2 | pages = 519–525. | doi = 10.1182/blood-2003-08-2743 | url = http://bloodjournal.hematologylibrary.org/cgi/content/abstract/104/2/519 | accessdate = 2010-12-15 | archive-date = 2010-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100722194515/http://bloodjournal.hematologylibrary.org/cgi/content/abstract/104/2/519 | dead-url = no }}</ref>患者有效。[[FDA|FDA]]已经批准三氧化二砷用于治疗[[急性早幼粒细胞白血病|急性早幼粒细胞白血病]]（APL）。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1016/j.apsb.2011.12.007|title=Developing new drugs from annals of Chinese medicine|year=2012|last1=Bian|first1=Zhaoxiang|last2=Chen|first2=Shilin|last3=Cheng|first3=Chungwah|last4=Wang|first4=Jun|last5=Xiao|first5=Haitao|last6=Qin|first6=Hongyan|journal=Acta Pharmaceutica Sinica B|volume=2|pages=1|name-list-format=vanc}}</ref>

[[甲基胂酸|甲基胂酸]]（CH<sub>3</sub>AsO(OH)<sub>2</sub>）是生产用于水稻和棉花的[[杀真菌剂|杀真菌剂]]田安（[[甲胂酸铁铵|甲胂酸铁铵]]）的[[前体|前体]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dict.chemyq.com/En/xz/xz1/5343bxeeb.htm|title=MAFA;Mongare liquid;Monkil liquid;Neoasozin liquid|accessdate=2015-08-01|archive-date=2019-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915232207/http://dict.chemyq.com/En/xz/xz1/5343bxeeb.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{link-en|苯胂酸|Phenylarsonic acid}}（C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>AsO(OH)<sub>2</sub>）的衍生物（包括[[洛克沙砷|洛克沙砷]]和[[对氨基苯胂酸|对氨基苯胂酸]]）用作牲畜的饲料添加剂。<ref name=FDAQ&A>{{cite news | author = U.S. Food and Drug Administration | url = http://www.fda.gov/AnimalVeterinary/SafetyHealth/ProductSafetyInformation/ucm258313.htm | title = Questions and answers regarding 3-nitro (roxarsone) | date = 8 Jun 2011 | accessdate = 2015-08-01 | archive-date = 2015-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150729165226/http://www.fda.gov/AnimalVeterinary/SafetyHealth/ProductSafetyInformation/ucm258313.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref> 因为会向环境中排放可溶性砷，这些用途有不少争议<ref>{{cite news | author = Institute for Agriculture and Trade Policy | url = http://www.iatp.org/documents/playing-chicken-avoiding-arsenic-in-your-meat | title = Playing Chicken: Avoiding Arsenic in Your Meat | date = April 4, 2006 | accessdate = 2015-08-01 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061537/http://www.iatp.org/documents/playing-chicken-avoiding-arsenic-in-your-meat | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Consumer Reports | url = http://www.consumerreports.org/cro/magazine/2012/11/arsenic-in-your-food/index.htm | title = Arsenic in your food | date = November 2012 | accessdate = 2015-08-01 | archive-date = 2014-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140308144211/http://www.consumerreports.org/cro/magazine/2012/11/arsenic-in-your-food/index.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，生产方已主动要求美国[[FDA|FDA]]撤销这些药物的许可证。<ref name=FDA2013>{{cite news | author = U.S. Food and Drug Administration | url = http://www.fda.gov/AnimalVeterinary/SafetyHealth/ProductSafetyInformation/ucm370568.htm | title = FDA response to citizen petition on arsenic-based animal drugs | date = 1 Oct 2013 | accessdate = 2015-08-01 | archive-date = 2015-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150814171323/http://www.fda.gov/AnimalVeterinary/SafetyHealth/ProductSafetyInformation/ucm370568.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 砷的甲基化 ==

无机砷及其化合物进入[[食物链|食物链]]后通过一系列[[甲基化|甲基化]]过程逐步[[代谢|代谢]]。<ref name='Biomethylation'/>该甲基化过程通过交替的[[还原反应|还原反应]]和[[氧化反应|氧化]][[甲基化|甲基化]]反应进行，即把五价砷还原为三价砷然后加上[[甲基|甲基]]（CH<sub>3</sub>）。<ref name='IARC'>{{cite journal | title = Arsenic in Drinking Water - Review article | journal = IARC Monographs - World Health Organization | volume = 84 | pages = 133–135 | url = http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Monographs/vol84/mono84-6.pdf | accessdate = 2011-01-10 | archive-date = 2012-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120304063926/http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Monographs/vol84/mono84-6.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>虽然总体上这是一个解毒过程，<ref name='IARC'/>但必须注意过程中多个[[甲基化|甲基化]]步骤产生的中间产物可能增加砷的毒性。<ref name=Seven>{{cite journal | pmc=1241242| year=2002| author1=Stýblo| first1=M.| title=The role of biomethylation in toxicity and carcinogenicity of arsenic: A research update| journal=Environmental Health Perspectives| volume=110| issue=Suppl 5| pages=767–771| last2=Drobná| first2=Z.| last3=Jaspers| first3=I.| last4=Lin| first4=S.| last5=Thomas| first5=D. J.| pmid=12426129}}</ref> 这是因为甲基胂能强效[[酶抑制剂|抑制]][[谷胱甘肽过氧化物酶|谷胱甘肽过氧化物酶]]、[[谷胱甘肽还原酶|谷胱甘肽还原酶]]、<ref>{{cite journal| last1=Chouchane| first1=S.| last2=Snow| first2=E. T.| last3=Snow| first3=E. T.| title=In vitro effect of arsenical compounds on glutathione-related enzymes| journal=Chem. Res. Toxicol| volume=4| issue=2| pages=517–22| pmid=12441363| url=http://toxsci.oxfordjournals.org/content/70/2/183.full| year=2002| access-date=2015-07-30| archive-date=2016-10-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161004165302/http://toxsci.oxfordjournals.org/content/70/2/183.full| dead-url=no}}</ref> [[丙酮酸脱氢酶|丙酮酸脱氢酶]]<ref name=Seven>{{cite journal | doi =10.1021/tx000264z| pmid =11409934| title =Monomethylarsonous Acid (MMA<sup>III</sup>) and Arsenite:  LD<sub>50</sub>in Hamsters and in Vitro Inhibition of Pyruvate Dehydrogenase| journal =Chemical Research in Toxicology| volume =14| issue =6| pages =651–656| year =2001| last1 =Petrick| first1 =Jay S.| last2 =Jagadish| first2 =Bhumasamudram| last3 =Mash| first3 =Eugene A.| last4 =Aposhian| first4 =H. Vasken}}</ref> 和[[硫氧还蛋白还原酶|硫氧还蛋白还原酶]]。<ref>{{cite journal| last1=Lin| first1=Lin S.| last2=Thomas| first2=D. J.| last3=Cullen| first3=W. R.| last4=Wang| first4=C.| last5=Styblo| first5=M.| last6=Del Razo| first6=L. M.| title=Arsenicals inhibit thioredoxin reductase in cultured rat hepatocytes| journal=Chem. Res. Toxicol| volume=14| issue=3| pages=305–11| pmid=11258980| year=2001}}</ref>

